{"tid":2334674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來終審全部睇太公文匯fake news，真係over dead body","createTime":"2020-12-21T10:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:18:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb6d6b52872bc8e17921c0511295f2ab036f2ac","tid":2334674,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/449027379815140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnostakemedicalstudent%2Fposts%2F449027379815140&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=09194fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/449027379815140</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNo Stake 醫學生<br />\n<br />\n【 終審法院淪為《大公報》老屈抗爭者，真相完全相反。 】<br />\n終審法院今日裁決緊急法及禁蒙面法合憲，判辭中有呢一句作理據，&quot;stopping motorists and extorting mobile phones or money by threatening to damage their vehicles&quot;，指示威者攔路並向司機勒索金錢同手機。<br />\n未盲目嘅香港人都睇到一到霧水，唔知幾時出現過呢啲場面。原來，出處黎自（最可靠嘅）《大公報》社論指「曱甴路霸攔車 劫買路錢」，「攞走咗佢銀包內5000元現金，狂言革命成功十倍奉還」。<br />\n<br />\n只要大家唔係同終審法院尊貴法官們一樣咁迷信《大公報》嘅話，都知道以上毫無證據嘅指控都係笑話，唔使我係度反駁。<br />\n我反而諗起上年一幕好少人留意到嘅場面。<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n八月十一號，示威者佔據紅隧，《大公報》同法官們口中嘅「劫攔路錢」冇出現，示威者反而重演烏克蘭Winter On Fire嘅一幕，大叫「免費過！」，同平時堵路嘅行為大為不同，比司機們直接駛經紅隧。呢一幕同《大公報》嘅老屈唔同，有片有真相，有直播影像紀錄哂落黎。<br />\n呢一幕，再一次證明抗爭手足所做嘅一切都係有理有據出師有名。示威者抗爭，雖然無可避免對巿民造成一定阻礙，但出處點從來都係對準政權，為左爭取百萬香港人共同相信嘅五大訴求。示威者佔據紅隧，本身大可以學《大公報》講咁為自己嘅私利勒索金錢。偏偏佢地係咁短嘅時間，變化莫測嘅環境中作出正確決定，比司機免費過。<br />\n<br />\n「免費過」，係因為佢地明白佔據紅隧嘅目的只係為左打擊不義政權嘅管治，所以靠住比司機免費駛過政府管理同擁有嘅紅隧，去影響政府稅收，同時間儘量減低對巿民嘅影響。<br />\nTaxation without representation is tyranny. 抗爭者有咁嘅智慧去明白呢一點，所以用佢地嘅行動還富於民，呢一個行動盡顯左佢地有勇亦有謀，智慧勇氣永不滅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">偏偏終審法院尊貴嘅法官，迷信《大公報》，愚笨可笑至此。</span></strong><br />\n&mdash;<br />\n(1) 城巿廣播<br />\n【810 紅磡】示威者到達紅磡海底隧道後 讓經紅隧的汽車免費通過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=724165814712295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D724165814712295&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=7cb7e0c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=724165814712295</a><br />\n(2) 誌報導 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2879615508721572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2879615508721572&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=251e544a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2879615508721572</a><br />\n(3)【逆權運動】抗爭者免費放車<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190811/ZYFWH426V62EJMQQ6CTMWLDCHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190811%2FZYFWH426V62EJMQQ6CTMWLDCHM%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=a9a52b0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190811%2FZYFWH426V62EJMQQ6CTMWLDCHM%2F&h=5cd59f55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190811/ZYFWH426V62EJMQQ6CTMWLDCHM/</a><br />\n(4) 大公報報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/.../2019/1007/358333.html...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2F...%2F2019%2F1007%2F358333.html...&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=da2d6501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/.../2019/1007/358333.html...</a>"},{"pid":"1abfa13db14cb78265e0b50b6f0f0d3f6f88f4b0","tid":2334674,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"over my dead body講幾句丫"},{"pid":"6842ee8e39078010c9acc96b930531a55ee72385","tid":2334674,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b303e442c2ef48b561736c16d380f4ab084c2515","tid":2334674,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"終審大法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif